# Large source assets used to generate the committed cubemap faces.
# Keep the 6 final JPGs in git; keep the EXR sources / intermediates out.
# Patterns match both the original root location (pre-react-port) and
# the public/ location used by the Next.js build.
**/assets/stars/raw/
**/assets/stars/*.exr
**/assets/stars/*.tif
**/assets/stars/cube_strip*
.vercel

